  "title": "Quantity Surveyor #76393",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Building & Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Quantity Surveyor</strong></li><li>Working Location: Islandwide</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Monday – Friday 8AM – 5PM, Saturday half day)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $4,500 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare detailed cost estimates and budgets for construction projects based on drawings, specifications, and site requirements</li><li>Manage contracts with subcontractors, suppliers, and clients, ensuring all terms and conditions are met.</li><li>Coordinate and evaluate tender submissions, obtain quotations, and prepare tender documents for projects</li><li>Monitor project costs, track variations, and provide regular cost reports to ensure projects remain within budget</li><li>Prepare and process interim valuations, progress claims, and manage payments to subcontractors and suppliers</li><li>Measure quantities and prepare bills of quantities, schedules, and other required documentation</li><li>Compile and present regular cost, progress, and financial reports as required by management.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Quantity Surveying or any equivalent discipline</li><li>Minimum 1-2 years of construction experience is preferred</li><li>Experience of civil engineering works such as road works, earthworks, drainage works are an added advantage</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76393 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
